# Cloud sync is OPTIONAL. With these unset, the app runs fully local — no
# accounts, no network, nothing leaves the device.
#
# To enable optional accounts + cross-device sync, create a free Supabase
# project and copy these from Settings -> API. Both are safe to expose in a
# public client app — Row-Level Security on the backend protects each user's
# data. Set them locally in a .env file (gitignored) and, for the live site,
# as GitHub repo variables of the same names (see SCOPE.md / the deploy workflow).
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
